Cougars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fredette first captured the national spotlight at BYU, where his sharpshooting and prolific scoring ability earned him the 2011 Naismith Player of the Year award and the cover of Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\", \"score\": 0.9856774638731407, \"rank\": 0.01312152768330427, \"text\": \"BYU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\"}, {\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.260770626602795e-30, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being selected 10th overall in the NBA Draft, Fredette's professional career in the United States was a rollercoaster, spanning five franchises over six seasons without finding a lasting fit.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0907567788607782e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fredette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\"}, {\"begi